{"tid":856901,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"一填東大嶼,全球財經風水大毀滅!三大指數大跌 道指收市瀉831點","createTime":"2018-10-10T23:45:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-10T23:45:00.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"406642865d4a457a5015c79318dcb72afa2d0a67","tid":856901,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-10T23:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181011/58780715\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F58780715&d=UOW%2B3jzwuZjdo5wYyXMmsQRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=18dbdf79\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181011%2F58780715&h=567686ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181011/58780715</a><br />\n<br />\n美國10年期債息持續高企，加上龍頭科技股下跌，拖累美股三大指數周三全線下跌，道瓊斯工業平均指數收<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">跌831.83點</span>，跌幅3.15%，報25598點。標普500指數跌94.66點，跌幅3.29%，報2785點。納斯達克綜合指數跌315.97點，跌幅4.08%，報7422點。<br />\n美股尾市恐慌拋售加劇，科技股領跌，納指暴跌4.08%；道指跌超800點，皆創8個月最大單日跌幅；標普500指數則挫3.27%，至2個月新低，連跌五日創2016年11月來最長連跌。<br />\n美股股王亞馬遜暴跌6.15%，單日市值蒸發超500億美元。在美國上市的中資概大跌，阿里巴巴下跌5.8%。<br />\n另一邊廂，紐約及布蘭特油價跌超過2%。美債孳息率漲勢重燃，10年期息曾攀升至3.22%。<br />\n今次是美股8個月來最大跌幅，總統特朗普乘機再批評聯邦儲備局加息步伐太快，指聯儲局「瘋了」。<br />\n<br />\n700 今日 10 cent 一手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}